---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="慈溪杨梅 - 夏日甜蜜果实" 
  description="慈溪杨梅以其果大、色艳、汁多、味美而闻名于世。产自浙江慈溪，千年种植历史，富含营养，是夏日不可或缺的美味佳品。"
>
  <!-- Hero Banner -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-bg"></div>
    <div class="hero-content">
      <h1>慈溪杨梅</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">江南珍果 · 红玉满枝</p>
      <p class="desc">产自东海之滨的千年古邑，汲取江南山水之灵气<br/>成就这一颗夏日至味</p>
    </div>
    <div class="scroll-hint">
      <span>向下滑动</span>
      <div class="arrow"></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- QR Code Section -->
  <section class="qr-section">
    <div class="qr-content">
      <h2>扫码下单</h2>
      <p>新鲜采摘，顺丰冷链直发<br/>足不出户尝到慈溪正宗东魁杨梅</p>
      <div class="qr-wrapper">
        <img src="https://api.qrserver.com/v1/create-qr-code/?size=200x200&data=https://ruoqianfengshao.github.io/yangmei-site&margin=10" alt="下单二维码" />
        <p class="qr-tip">手机扫码访问网站下单</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- History Section -->
  <section class="content-section" id="history">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-badge">历史</div>
      <h2>千年种植史</h2>
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="section-text">
          <p>慈溪杨梅的栽培历史可追溯至<span class="highlight">唐代</span>，距今已逾千年。慈溪地处北纬30°的黄金气候带，三面环山、一面临海，形成独特的"小气候"环境，非常适宜杨梅生长。</p>
          <p>宋代《本草纲目》中已有记载，慈溪杨梅作为贡品进献朝廷。明清时期，慈溪杨梅已远销海外，成为海上丝绸之路的重要物产之一。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-img">
          <div class="img-placeholder">
            <span>历史图片</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Culture Section -->
  <section class="content-section alt" id="culture">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-badge">文化</div>
      <h2>江南梅文化</h2>
      <div class="section-body reverse">
        <div class="section-text">
          <p>在慈溪，杨梅不仅是一种水果，更是一种<span class="highlight">文化符号</span>。每年六月杨梅成熟季节，当地会举办盛大的"杨梅节"，吸引数以万计的游客前来采摘体验。</p>
          <p>"慈溪杨梅酒"是当地的传统酿品，采用古法酿制，酒体红润，果香四溢。此外还有杨梅干、杨梅酱等特色加工品，承载着慈溪人对这片土地的深厚情感。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-img">
          <div class="img-placeholder">
            <span>文化图片</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Botany Section -->
  <section class="content-section" id="botany">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="section-badge">植物学</div>
      <h2>杨梅的植物学奥秘</h2>
      <div class="section-body">
        <div class="section-text">
          <p>杨梅（<em>Myrica rubra</em>）属于杨梅科杨梅属，是常绿乔木，树高可达5-15米。其果实呈球形，直径1-3厘米，表面密布细密肉柱，成熟时呈紫红色或白色。</p>
          <p>慈溪杨梅的主栽品种为<span class="highlight">"东魁"</span>和"荸荠种"，其中东魁果实最大，单果重可达30克以上，含糖量高达12-15%，酸甜适口，品质极佳。</p>
          <p>杨梅树根系与放线菌共生，能固定空气中的氮气，因此杨梅树特别耐贫瘠，也被称为"肥料树"。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="section-img">
          <div class="img-placeholder">
            <span>植物学图片</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Footer -->
  <footer class="footer">
    <p>© 2026 慈溪杨梅 · 东海古邑，江南梅香</p>
  </footer>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Hero */
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    height: 100vh;
    min-height: 600px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  
  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: 
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 20%, rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.3) 0%, transparent 50%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 80%, rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.2) 0%, transparent 50%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #1a0a0a 0%, #2d1810 50%, #1a0505 100%);
    z-index: 0;
  }
  
  .hero-bg::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: 
      radial-gradient(circle at 20% 50%, rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.15) 0%, transparent 25%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 80% 30%, rgba(142, 68, 173, 0.1) 0%, transparent 20%),
      radial-gradient(circle at 50% 80%, rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.1) 0%, transparent 25%);
    animation: pulse 8s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.6; }
  }
  
  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fff;
  }
  
  .hero-content h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 10vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.3em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    text-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.5);
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out;
  }
  
  .subtitle {
    font-size: clamp(1.2rem, 3vw, 1.8rem);
    color: #e74c3c;
    letter-spacing: 0.5em;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.2s both;
  }
  
  .desc {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    line-height: 2;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.4s both;
  }
  
  @keyframes fadeInUp {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(30px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }
  
  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 3rem;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    animation: fadeInUp 1s ease-out 0.6s both;
  }
  
  .arrow {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    border-right: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    border-bottom: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    transform: rotate(45deg);
    animation: bounce 2s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  
  @keyframes bounce {
    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(45deg); }
    50% { transform: translateY(8px) rotate(45deg); }
  }

  /* QR Section */
  .qr-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #1a0505 0%, #2d1810 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }
  
  .qr-content h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  
  .qr-content p {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .qr-wrapper {
    display: inline-flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
  
  .qr-wrapper img {
    width: 180px;
    height: 180px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    background: #fff;
    padding: 12px;
    box-shadow: 0 0 40px rgba(192, 57, 43, 0.3);
  }
  
  .qr-tip {
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  /* Content Sections */
  .content-section {
    padding: 6rem 2rem;
    background: #fff;
  }
  
  .content-section.alt {
    background: #f8f5f2;
  }
  
  .section-inner {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  
  .section-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.4rem 1.2rem;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #c0392b, #e74c3c);
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    border-radius: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .section-inner h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);
    color: #1a1a1a;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }
  
  .section-body {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }
  
  .section-body.reverse {
    direction: rtl;
  }
  
  .section-body.reverse > * {
    direction: ltr;
  }
  
  .section-text p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: #555;
    line-height: 2;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .highlight {
    color: #c0392b;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  
  .section-img {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  
  .img-placeholder {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 350px;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e8e0da, #d4c8be);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    color: #8b7355;
    font-size: 1rem;
  }
  
  /* Footer */
  .footer {
    padding: 2rem;
    background: #1a0a0a;
    text-align: center;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }
  
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .section-body {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2rem;
    }
    
    .section-body.reverse {
      direction: ltr;
    }
    
    .qr-wrapper img {
      width: 150px;
      height: 150px;
    }
  }
</style>